Field Type Constraint <code>axes</code> object (map of string to string[]) Each key maps to an array of option values <p>Each axis key/value pair generates a combinatorial expansion. For example:</p> <pre><code>"matrix": {
  "axes": {
    "opt": ["/Od", "/O1", "/O2", "/Ox"],
    "arch": ["/arch:IA32", "/arch:SSE"]
  }
}
</code></pre> <p>This generates 8 experiments (4 optimizations × 2 architecture flags) per profile.</p> <p>Warning</p> <p><code>max_experiments</code> caps the total number of experiments that will be run. If the full matrix exceeds the limit, the lab is truncated.</p>
